briefTitle: Olive Oil for High Risk Breast Cancer Prevention in Women
officialTitle: A Pilot Study of Hydroxytyrosol, a Component of Olive Oil for Breast Cancer Prevention In Women At High Risk Of Breast Cancer
summary: This is a pilot study evaluating the effect of hydroxytyrosol, a component of olive oil, on mammographic density in women at high risk of developing breast cancer.

primaryOutcome.measure: Change in Maximum Volumetric Breast Density Percentage
